; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 114-117, 182-190
; Tests the error when two null postings exist and one account name ends
; with a special character (digit, ), }, ]), suggesting a misspelling.
; account_ends_with_special_char checks for these patterns.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food2
    Expenses:Rent
    Assets:Cash               $-50.00

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 9:
Error: Posting with null amount's account may be misspelled:
  "Expenses:Food2"
end test
